---
import Star from "./icons/star.astro";
import Diamond from "./icons/diamond.astro";
import Rumble from "./icons/rumble.astro";
---

<section id="services" class="section pb-12 md:pb-28">
  <h2 class="container mb-8 animate-fade-in-up animate-duration-1000">
    Servicios
  </h2>

  <div
    class="group lg:hover:bg-primary border-y-2 animate-fade-in-right animate-duration-1000 duration-1000 ease-in-out"
  >
    <div
      class="container grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 px-2 py-8 md:py-12 xl:py-14"
    >
      <dt class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3 xl:p-0 lg:group-hover:text-secondary"
        >
          <Star
            class="size-6 md:size-8 fill-primary lg:group-hover:fill-secondary"
          />
          <h3>Desarrollo Web</h3>
        </div>
        <svg
          class="size-7 md:size-10 fill-primary lg:hidden"
          viewBox="0 0 512 512"
          ><polygon
            points="396.6,160 416,180.7 256,352 96,180.7 115.3,160 256,310.5 "
          ></polygon>
        </svg>
      </dt>
      <dd class="text lg md:text-xl text-secondary hidden lg:group-hover:block">
        Creo sitios web únicos con código adaptados a cada dispositivo. Me
        concentro en el rendimiento, la accesibilidad y las animaciones
        atractivas.
      </dd>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="group lg:hover:bg-primary animate-fade-in-right animate-duration-1000 duration-1000 ease-in-out"
  >
    <div
      class="container grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 py-8 px-2 md:py-12 xl:py-14"
    >
      <dt class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3 xl:p-0 lg:group-hover:text-secondary"
        >
          <Rumble
            class="size-6 md:size-8 fill-primary lg:group-hover:fill-secondary"
          />
          <h3>Diseño Web</h3>
        </div>
        <svg
          class="size-7 md:size-10 fill-primary lg:hidden"
          viewBox="0 0 512 512"
          ><polygon
            points="396.6,160 416,180.7 256,352 96,180.7 115.3,160 256,310.5 "
          ></polygon>
        </svg>
      </dt>
      <dd class="text lg md:text-xl text-secondary hidden lg:group-hover:block">
        Diseño sitios web con una tipografía limpia y diseños minimalistas que
        atraen tu marca y cumplen con los objetivos comerciales.
      </dd>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="group lg:hover:bg-primary border-y-2 animate-fade-in-right animate-duration-1000 duration-1000 ease-in-out"
  >
    <div
      class="container grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 py-8 px-2 md:py-12 2xl:py-14 items-center"
    >
      <dt class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3 2xl:p-0 lg:group-hover:text-secondary"
        >
          <Diamond
            class="size-6 md:size-8 fill-primary lg:group-hover:fill-secondary"
          />
          <h3>SEO</h3>
        </div>
        <svg
          class="size-7 md:size-10 fill-primary lg:hidden"
          viewBox="0 0 512 512"
          ><polygon
            points="396.6,160 416,180.7 256,352 96,180.7 115.3,160 256,310.5 "
          ></polygon>
        </svg>
      </dt>
      <dd class="text lg md:text-xl text-secondary hidden lg:group-hover:block">
        Optimizo la presencia en línea para elevar la visibilidad en los
        rankings de búsqueda para que sus voces puedan ser escuchadas en el
        mundo digital.
      </dd>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
